#NAME The Office of the Guardian Leader
#DESCRIPTION This walls and floors of this office are made of the same gray marble as
the rest of the Hall of Law.  A shelf in the back stands for the filing of
paperwork and a solid oaken desk sits in the center of the chamber.  A small
blue orb lies on the surface of the desk, mounted on a base of gossamer
